WEBVTT

00:03.775 --> 00:06.244
Ants on a log. You'll love 'em.

00:06.486 --> 00:08.329
Hey, I'm not eating ants.

00:08.571 --> 00:09.882
Not real ants, duh.

00:09.906 --> 00:11.541
Raisins and peanut
butter and celery.

00:12.033 --> 00:13.376
It's my best dish...

00:13.451 --> 00:14.345
I think.

00:14.369 --> 00:15.586
You'll see.

00:19.666 --> 00:22.427
Hey, crank it up. People in
Sausalito can't hear it.

00:25.630 --> 00:27.473
What the hell do you
think you're doing?

00:28.299 --> 00:29.600
Charlie!

00:29.634 --> 00:30.935
God!

00:32.052 --> 00:33.604
- Jeez...
- Charlie, get out of here!

00:33.805 --> 00:35.408
You can't just come busting
in my room like that!

00:35.432 --> 00:37.317
Claudia's downstairs,
for God's sakes.

00:37.350 --> 00:39.495
Claudia's downstairs all the
time when you and Kirsten do it.

00:39.519 --> 00:41.330
- That's not the same thing.
- That's exactly the same.

00:41.354 --> 00:43.040
Claudia's downstairs,
you're 16 years old,

00:43.064 --> 00:44.458
and you're not having
sex in this house.

00:44.482 --> 00:45.835
You had sex in this
house when you were 16.

00:45.859 --> 00:46.752
No, I didn't!

00:46.776 --> 00:48.379
Mom and Dad made it
impossible for me,

00:48.403 --> 00:49.630
I'm gonna make it
impossible for you.

00:49.654 --> 00:50.872
Oh, like that's fair.

00:53.324 --> 00:54.677
Close your eyes and
stick out your tongue.

00:54.701 --> 00:56.303
Ants on a log. Here you go.

00:56.327 --> 00:58.463
Claud, let's, um, eat them
in the kitchen, okay?

00:59.289 --> 01:00.590
Okay.

01:02.876 --> 01:04.302
You happy?

01:04.419 --> 01:05.762
Wow...

01:06.004 --> 01:08.389
must be cool to have a
cop for a big brother.

01:08.590 --> 01:09.817
Hey, Jill, this
isn't your place.

01:09.841 --> 01:11.027
When you go to someone
else's place,

01:11.051 --> 01:11.944
they've got rules.

01:11.968 --> 01:13.279
Charlie, I always
thought you were cool.

01:13.303 --> 01:14.947
Isn't that what you're
always saying, Bailey?

01:14.971 --> 01:16.647
"How cool Charlie is?"

01:19.976 --> 01:20.995
I found some raisins,

01:21.019 --> 01:23.154
but I had to dig them
out of the Raisin Bran.

01:24.314 --> 01:25.782
You want an ants on a log?

01:25.982 --> 01:27.200
Um...

01:29.027 --> 01:30.787
Uh, I'm leaving.

01:31.362 --> 01:33.007
I'm leaving, okay?
I get the message.

01:33.031 --> 01:34.499
You don't have to tell me twice.

01:35.283 --> 01:36.709
Earthquake!

